{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-02710/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-02710"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:27:10"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["plan américain"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, pan, tilt"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["low key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman enters the atelier from the top of the stairs."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-02710","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-02710"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/canvas/1/46acffdf-56ec-4d16-8cab-014d0cf3a702","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T15:04:43.567Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Cyril makes her entrance next to <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW2029470 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.tate.org.uk/art/artworks/john-young-woman-holding-a-black-cat-n05744\"><u>a painting of a woman</u></a>. Again, the female figures of the film are closely associated with artistic creations. Cyril, in this case, is linked to the staid form of a portrait.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:102.07267833109017,784.8452220726783,567.21399730821,248.07537012113062"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/canvas/1/ffd616b0-4fa0-4433-863f-82e5a19cb415","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T15:05:03.182Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Cyril’s shadow bobs up the stairs as she approaches the attic. But as she rounds the top step, her body slows, startled by the fact that Reynolds isn’t alone. Her face remains in the shadows, making it hard to discern her expression as she registers Alma’s presence in the room.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02710/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:802.3687752355316,132.3553162853298,368.23687752355306,346.27187079407804"}}}]}]}]}